    <id>workflow_media_converter</id>
    <name>Automated Media Conversion</name>
    <summary>Rule based conversion of Video/Audio files via FFmpeg</summary>
    <description>An app to trigger automatic conversion of media using FFmpeg.  Based on user defined rules, media conversion jobs will be dispatched in the background.  A common use case is for converting videos uploaded from iPhones in Apple Quicktime format to MP4 so that those videos can be played in non-Apple browsers.</description>
